WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.577 --> 00:00:01.829
Good morning, family!

00:00:01.829 --> 00:00:03.356
How are y'all doing?

00:00:03.356 --> 00:00:09.109
I just wanted to say thank you all for all the kindness.

00:00:09.700 --> 00:00:12.525
We're at this prayer conference right now, still in our hotel.

00:00:12.525 --> 00:00:33.583
We've been here for two days, and many of you traveled to see Sister Billye and support her ministry.

00:00:33.583 --> 00:00:58.710
We want to say thank you to all the subscribers who said they came here because of what we said to support Sister Billye.

00:00:58.710 --> 00:01:10.820
The prayer conference has been amazing and such a blessing.

00:01:11.240 --> 00:01:51.867
I want to say to all of you who traveled so far—from Chicago, New York, Los Angeles, and all over the United States—to support this conference and pray for our nation: God bless you all.

00:01:51.867 --> 00:02:11.320
I know it took a lot of time, effort, resources, and money for hotels and food.

00:02:13.779 --> 00:02:44.628
I know some of you spent thousands to do this, and I know God is an abundant supplier who will reward you for helping pray for our nation.

00:02:44.628 --> 00:02:53.640
Thank you for supporting Sister Billye and the family.

00:02:53.640 --> 00:03:06.760
They are some of the nicest people I have ever met.

00:03:06.760 --> 00:03:16.355
Seriously, y'all, they are genuinely nice people.

00:03:16.355 --> 00:03:46.890
Sometimes you get around Christians in upper leadership and you think they might be stuck up, but these people are really good people.

00:03:46.890 --> 00:04:01.368
I've been really impressed with how kind they've been to us.

00:04:08.706 --> 00:04:08.960
I'm grateful for their love toward my family.

00:04:08.960 --> 00:04:42.985
She let me talk last night about the prophetic words the Lord is showing me, and we prayed against some of the things the Lord showed me.

00:04:42.985 --> 00:05:00.840
It is amazing to see what the Lord has done in this amount of time.

00:05:03.690 --> 00:05:29.337
I felt like we were one of those big mega-ships plowing through the ice in the spirit realm concerning President Trump and the election.

00:05:29.337 --> 00:05:44.622
I could feel the shifting in the spirit as we were praying and interceding.

00:05:56.770 --> 00:06:03.485
It felt like we were plowing through demonic strongholds with so many seasoned prayer warriors.

00:06:03.485 --> 00:06:13.576
There are a lot of people standing for this nation.

00:06:22.960 --> 00:06:38.651
I believe beyond a shadow of a doubt that Trump is going to win this election and we're going to see victory.

00:06:38.651 --> 00:06:58.340
As Sister Lynn said today, 'Do not become complacent after you see the victory.

00:06:58.340 --> 00:07:33.102
' We have got to keep our foot on the gas and keep on praying over the cabinet and his decisions on who he surrounds himself with.

00:07:33.102 --> 00:08:00.039
We pray that he puts Godly men and women in positions of counsel so that when he wins, it will be by a landslide.

00:08:11.628 --> 00:08:21.496
We are also believing that God will take the House and the Senate for a supernatural move.

00:08:21.496 --> 00:08:37.924
The next four years should be smooth so that we can have a revival.

00:08:37.924 --> 00:08:55.833
We prayed about the financial collapse and the things the Lord showed me.

00:09:04.589 --> 00:09:17.632
I still feel something in the natural, but I am not moved by what I see or feel.

00:09:17.632 --> 00:09:38.171
I still have a caution and feel we have prayer to do concerning the economy.

00:09:38.171 --> 00:10:03.879
When I gave the word about the economy, the Lord rebuked me and said, 'Brandon, you need to tell My people do not fear.

00:10:03.879 --> 00:10:28.383
' He said, 'I will supply all your needs according to My riches in glory by Christ Jesus.

00:10:28.383 --> 00:10:52.279
' This is not for the believer; He said He will provide for His beloved.

00:10:52.279 --> 00:11:27.618
If you're a tither and a giver and believe that Jesus is your Jehovah Jireh, He will provide for you regardless of whether the bottom falls out tomorrow.

00:11:27.618 --> 00:11:52.664
I was looking at statistics today, and a news article stated that in the last three weeks, we've spent half a trillion dollars more in the deficit.

00:11:52.664 --> 00:11:58.640
It was skyrocketing on the graph.

00:11:58.640 --> 00:12:09.439
Our national debt is $35 trillion now.

00:12:09.439 --> 00:12:16.549
Are we moved by fear?

00:12:16.549 --> 00:12:26.624
No, but we know the signs of the times.

00:12:34.690 --> 00:12:47.510
The dollar is in the way; they have to take it down to bring in the one-world government and the digital platform.

00:12:54.742 --> 00:13:03.095
We can lessen the effect so that it will not affect you.

00:13:04.555 --> 00:13:28.267
I want you to be prepared spiritually, interceding for your house and listening to Him on how to intercede for our nation.

00:13:28.267 --> 00:13:38.296
We don't get into fear; we walk in faith.

00:13:38.296 --> 00:13:54.173
That's why I brought up food supplies and the dollar crash.

00:13:54.173 --> 00:14:16.933
I heard a testimony about people during the Great Depression who were consistent tithers and never lacked a job or any good thing.

00:14:16.933 --> 00:14:51.405
My granny told me it was terrible; she was 106 when she died and said it was terrible going through the depression, but they weren't tithers then.

00:14:51.405 --> 00:15:12.780
However, I heard of people like Brother Kenneth Hagin who believed in their covenant and made it through.

00:15:12.780 --> 00:15:25.977
Regardless of what the economy does, God will turn it around for your favor.

00:15:31.975 --> 00:15:46.759
We are overcomers by the blood of the Lamb and the word of our testimony.

00:15:56.725 --> 00:16:16.679
If I ever come off as a fearmonger, I want to emphasize that there is always faith to believe yourself out of any trap the devil tries to set.

00:16:16.679 --> 00:16:29.668
Whatsoever a man soweth, that will he also reap.

00:16:29.668 --> 00:16:35.146
This week has been interesting.

00:16:35.146 --> 00:16:49.264
When we went to Billy Burke, three major words were given to my wife and me.

00:17:04.756 --> 00:17:17.769
We were praying for Megan, and I can see a supernatural change already taking place in her.

00:17:17.769 --> 00:17:33.270
She is talking more in the last 48 hours than we've ever heard in her whole life.

00:17:33.270 --> 00:17:45.508
After the man of God prayed, she used appropriate words at the right timing.

00:17:45.508 --> 00:17:58.325
She was even jabbering and chirping to the people in front of us.

00:18:01.600 --> 00:18:16.320
I think they got up and left because she was disruptive, but Megan was trying to make sentences.

00:18:18.714 --> 00:18:26.486
You can see the wheels turning in her eyes.

00:18:26.486 --> 00:18:32.244
There is a tangible turnaround.

00:18:32.244 --> 00:18:44.960
If you are believing for something, get submersed in God's word and do not go dry.

00:18:44.960 --> 00:19:00.382
Give God the glory over every small thing that happens because it builds into a miracle.

00:19:00.382 --> 00:19:20.309
Like when she got potty trained; the doctors told us we would more than likely never see this child be potty trained.

00:19:20.309 --> 00:19:42.940
Professionals tried to help us and it did not work; they said she would wear a diaper the rest of her life.

00:19:50.191 --> 00:19:50.422
But God is rich in mercy.

00:19:50.422 --> 00:20:00.320
We had a glimmer of hope like Noah's olive leaf.

00:20:00.320 --> 00:20:19.985
When he prayed for her the first time, we stood by faith, and now we have our second olive leaf.

00:20:19.985 --> 00:20:39.960
We are fully persuaded, just like Abraham, that what God has promised He is able also to perform.

00:20:39.960 --> 00:20:55.436
Even if it seems impossible, all things are possible to him that believes.

00:20:55.436 --> 00:21:06.920
We've been putting her in an environment of faith at these services.

00:21:06.920 --> 00:21:44.176
It's been stretching her to sit for two services a day, and she's been saying, 'Daddy, my heiny hurts,' but it's time for her to come out.

00:21:44.176 --> 00:22:01.102
Faith without works is dead, so we are putting our faith in action.

00:22:01.102 --> 00:22:11.749
Diana refuses to treat her as anything other than healed.

00:22:15.253 --> 00:22:19.090
We are resisting the symptoms.

00:22:19.090 --> 00:22:29.096
We're going to sit down in restaurants as a family now.

00:22:29.096 --> 00:22:38.434
For years, we sat in the car and ate drive-through food because she was so bound up, but now we are pushing her by faith.

00:22:38.434 --> 00:22:49.919
We are not accepting the symptoms of autism anymore.

00:22:49.919 --> 00:23:02.580
She points to the menu and tells us what she wants.

00:23:03.240 --> 00:23:04.480
It's amazing.

00:23:04.480 --> 00:23:13.509
The olive leaf is becoming an olive branch.

00:23:13.509 --> 00:23:22.629
We're standing for the whole tree.

00:23:37.577 --> 00:23:45.298
We have to have humor and laugh a little bit because a merry heart does good like a medicine.

00:24:04.684 --> 00:24:04.979
We just came on today to tell everybody what the Lord is doing.

00:24:05.864 --> 00:24:30.943
The first hotel air conditioner was not working, so we had to move, but God is faithful.

00:24:42.310 --> 00:24:42.600
We appreciate your prayers for Megan.

00:24:51.502 --> 00:25:00.810
So many people said they are interceding for her, and it really blessed me.

00:25:01.955 --> 00:25:21.177
I am not a celebrity; I'm just me, and I wish I could hear all your stories.

00:25:21.177 --> 00:25:28.679
Let's pray for your finances and healing.

00:25:28.679 --> 00:25:52.360
Father, we take authority over demonic spirits and thank You that by Your stripes we are healed.

00:26:00.284 --> 00:26:17.920
We believe for a red wave and that the House and Senate will remain red with a larger majority.

00:26:21.812 --> 00:26:35.790
We pray for Canada to remove Justin Trudeau and for them to have a righteous leader.

00:26:42.020 --> 00:26:57.148
We pray against illegal immigrants voting without voter IDs; Jay Sekulow put that out, and we stand against it.

00:26:57.148 --> 00:27:10.799
We believe for an uncovering of darkness and a vote without corruption or rioting.

00:27:10.799 --> 00:27:36.470
I'll try to be up in the foyer if I can, but I don't want to take from Billye's event or be disrespectful.

00:27:39.228 --> 00:27:47.600
We agree that you are healed and everything is turning around for your good.

00:27:47.600 --> 00:27:48.824
Amen.

00:27:48.824 --> 00:28:06.636
Please subscribe if you're new; I'll be more consistent with videos once I'm home and have better internet.

00:28:13.159 --> 00:28:14.359
God bless you all!
